{"tid":523418,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那內蒙殖民地政府自爆數據造假　工業增加值作大3500億","createTime":"2018-01-08T14:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T02:29:56.000Z","uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2cbbbef475ccc9408d675108c806269718278523","tid":523418,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T14:06:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/%E5%85%A7%E8%92%99%E8%87%AA%E7%88%86%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E9%80%A0%E5%81%87-%E5%B7%A5%E6%A5%AD%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E5%80%BC%E4%BD%9C%E5%A4%A73500%E5%84%84/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%2592%2599%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A%25E9%2580%25A0%25E5%2581%2587-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%25A2%259E%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%2580%25BC%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%25A4%25A73500%25E5%2584%2584%2F&d=S5hC4lpB7aC5S1kjtA%2FrcqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=3cd3c39c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%2592%2599%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A%25E9%2580%25A0%25E5%2581%2587-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%25A2%259E%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%2580%25BC%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%25A4%25A73500%25E5%2584%2584%2F&h=069d8c1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/china/%E5%85%A7%E8%92%99%E8%87%AA%E7%88%86%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E9%80%A0%E5%81%87-%E5%B7%A5%E6%A5%AD%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E5%80%BC%E4%BD%9C%E5%A4%A73500%E5%84%84/</a><br />\n<br />\n一年前，遼寧省省長陳求發在政府工作報告中，自爆該省在2011年至2014年造數，虛報財政收入及經濟數據，因而要上繳過多稅款，令該省人民平均每人多交稅千元。一年後再有地方政府自爆做數，新華社日前報道，內蒙自治區官員上周在一個工作會議揭露，於2016年作大工業增加值2900億元（人民幣 下同），相當約3500億港元，佔總數4成，連帶自治區政府的財政收入亦要減少530億元，佔總數26%，而2017年的預算公共財政收入亦調低14.4%。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，在上周三舉行的中共內蒙古自治區第十屆委員會第五次全體會議暨全區經濟工作會議，自治區黨委突然「自曝家醜」，透露政府的財政收入「虛增空轉」，部分旗縣區工業增加值存在水分。在財政審計部門反覆核算後，把2016年的一般公共預算收入調減530億元，2017年的預算公共財政收入亦調減14．4%。同時，經過初步認定，應該把2016年規模以上工業增加值調低2900億元，佔全部工業增加值的40%。<br />\n<br />\n政府高層又「坦承」，自治區已煞停不少基建項目，並明確提出利用3年時間，把政府債務率降到合理水平。<br />\n<br />\n報道形容呼和浩特市玉泉區書記吳文明「深有感觸」地説：「政府投資要量入為出，看菜吃飯，堅決防止盲目過度舉債，防止不負責任地制造風險，這些要求很實。」"},{"pid":"3a85143e137e0d0e431affc4e1c29cd75fdc3ad5","tid":523418,"uid":30169,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T14:08:12.000Z","msg":"垃圾係咁上下"},{"pid":"5bae8bc73f1942cfbacd8a506061163be5c6dc78","tid":523418,"uid":50328,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T14:14:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1906d4ae64a8a233e74857e429eabcddbbf2b3b9","tid":523418,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bae8bc73f1942cfbacd8a506061163be5c6dc78","tid":523418,"uid":50328,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T14:14:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T14:14:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee944faac69927fd466861c5b7de9ef2a3a7d80","tid":523418,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T14:16:59.000Z","msg":"鄰國呢d野好平常，唔造假先算新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c6d90d02a9f810d6b75a3dbc2af4538bb3022c","tid":523418,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T14:31:06.000Z","msg":"支那造假係新聞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7378ce26992f09cfce640f5458a68fb1226fe832","tid":523418,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T23:19:07.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a9f26f030c8f39077c5bc2586a63eb06aa7697d1","tid":523418,"uid":44118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1906d4ae64a8a233e74857e429eabcddbbf2b3b9","tid":523418,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bae8bc73f1942cfbacd8a506061163be5c6dc78","tid":523418,"uid":50328,"like":10,"dis